external_games.name: King of the Faridun Supporter Pack

name: Path of Exile: King of the Faridun Supporter Pack
summary: The King of the Faridun Supporter Pack contains Early Access to Path of Exile 2, two Armour Sets, two Back Attachments, a Level-up Effect, a Hideout, three Weapon Skins, three Pets, two Hideout Decorations, a Portal Effect, two Portrait Frames, two Forum Titles, two Badges, and 1000 Points.
